      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1905_AS_RBH_1_00052"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">Wien XVIII. Spoettelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr Richard Beer-Hofma<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>,</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb173" type="place">Rodaun</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">bei <rs ref="#pmb73" type="place">Liesing</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1905_AS_RBH_1_00053"/><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>, <date>30. 7. 905</date></dateline><salute>lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eit ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tern wieder daheim. Bleibe vorläufig. Das <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29999" subtype="implied">Stück</rs> von <rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Bahr</rs> hab
               ich Ihnen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chicken la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en.</p><p>Wo<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind Sie? Ist <rs ref="#pmb10860" type="person">Paula</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon ganz wohl? –</p><closer>Herzlichst, von uns <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">beiden</rs><lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
